        (
        V
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle \det(V)}
   is a divisor of 
  
    
      
        det
        (
        V
        )
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \det(V).}
   Indeed, let 
  
    
      
        p
      
    
    {\displaystyle p}
   be a polynomial with 
  
    
      
        
